 season|2009]]\n|[[2009 Major League Soccer season|MLS]]\n|30||12||7||11||38||29||47\n|3rd; Conf.<br>4th; Overall\n|[[2009 MLS Cup Playoffs#Western Conference|QF]]\n|bgcolor=\"gold\"|'''[[2009 U.S. Open Cup Final|Champions]]'''\n|\n|\n|align=\"left\"|[[Fredy Montero]]||12\n|-\n![[2010 Seattle Sounders FC season|2010]]\n|[[2010 Major League Soccer season|MLS]]\n|30||14||10||6||39||35||48\n|4th; Conf.<br>6th; Overall\n|[[2010 MLS Cup Playoffs#Conference Semifinals|QF]]\n|bgcolor=\"gold\"|'''[[2010 U.S. Open Cup Final|Champions]]'''\n|bgcolor=\"silver\"|[[Seattle Sounders FC Community Shield#The game|Runners-up]]\n|[[2010\u201311 CONCACAF Champions League Group Stage#Group C|GS]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Fredy Montero]]<br>[[Steve Zakuani]]||10\n|-\n![[2011 Seattle Sounders FC season|2011]]\n|[[2011 Major League Soccer season|MLS]]\n|34||18||7||9||56||37||63\n|''2nd; Conf.<br>2nd; Overall''\n|[[2011 MLS Cup Playoffs#Conference Semifinals|QF]]\n|bgcolor=\"gold\"|'''[[2011 U.S. Open Cup Final|Champions]]'''\n|bgcolor=\"gold\"|'''[[Seattle Sounders FC Community Shield|Champions]]'''\n|[[2011\u201312 CONCACAF Champions League|QF]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Fredy Montero]]||12\n|-\n![[2012 Seattle Sounders FC season|2012]]\n|[[2012 Major League Soccer season|MLS]]\n|34||15||8||11||51||33||56\n|''3rd; Conf.<br>7th; Overall''\n|[[2012 MLS Cup Playoffs#Conference Championships|SF]]\n|bgcolor=\"silver\"|[[2012 U.S. Open Cup Final|Runners-up]]\n|\n|[[2012\u201313 CONCACAF Champions League|SF]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Eddie Johnson (American soccer)|Eddie Johnson]]||14\n|-\n![[2013 Seattle Sounders FC season|2013]]\n|[[2013 Major League Soccer season|MLS]]\n|34||15||12||7||42||42||52\n|''4th; Conf.<br>6th; Overall''\n|[[2013 MLS Cup Playoffs#Conference Semifinals|QF]]\n|[[2013 U.S. Open Cup#Third Round|R3]]\n|\n|\n|align=\"left\"|[[Eddie Johnson (American soccer)|Eddie Johnson]]||9\n|-\n![[2014 Seattle Sounders FC season|2014]]\n|[[2014 Major League Soccer season|MLS]]\n|34||20||10||4||65||50||64\