st Actor \u2013 Television Series Drama|Best Actor in a Television Series \u2013 Drama]]\n|Timothy Hutton\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Satellite Award for Best Actress \u2013 Television Series Drama|Best Actress in a Television Series \u2013 Drama]]\n|Felicity Huffman\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Satellite Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Series, Miniseries or Television Film|Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Series, Miniseries or Television Film]]\n|Elvis Nolasco\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Satellite Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Series, Miniseries or Television Film|Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Series, Miniseries or Television Film]]\n|Regina King\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Satellite Award for Best Cast \u2013 Television Series|Best Ensemble \u2013 Television Series]]\n|Felicity Huffman, Timothy Hutton, W. Earl Brown, Regina King, Richard Cabral, Caitlin Gerard, Benito Martinez, Penelope Ann Miller, Elvis Nolasco, and Johnny Ortiz\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=5|[[NAACP Image Award|47th NAACP Image Awards]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/naacp-image-award-nominees-full-846814 |title='Creed,' 'Empire' Top NAACP Image Award Nominations; Full List |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=December 8, 2015 |accessdate=December 12, 2015}}</ref>\n|[[NAACP Image Award for Outstanding Television Movie, Mini-Series or Dramatic Special|Outstanding Television Movie, Mini-Series or Dramatic Special]]\n|''American Crime''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[NAACP Image Award for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series|Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series]]\n|Regina King\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Outstanding Director in a Drama Series\n|John Ridley <br> (Episode: \"Episode One\")\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[Millicent Shelton]] <br> (Episode: \"Episode Ten\")\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Outstanding Writer in a Drama Series\n|John Ridley <br> (Episode: \"Episode One\")\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=4|[[73rd Golden Globe Awards]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2016/01/10/golden-globe-award-winners-2016-full-list