017</center>\n| 2.67<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/tv-ratings-sunday-march-12-2017/|title='American Crime' premieres low, 'Chicago Justice' fairly steady: Sunday final ratings\".|last=Porter|first=Rick|date=March 13, 2017|accessdate=May 9, 2017|work=TV by the Numbers}}</ref>\n| style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:110%\"|<center>April 30, 2017</center>\n| 2.00<ref name=\"3.10\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/sunday-final-ratings-april-30-2017/|title='Chicago Justice,' 'America's Funniest Home Videos' adjust up: Sunday final ratings|last=Porter|first=Rick|work=TV by the Numbers|date=May 2, 2017|accessdate=May 9, 2017}}</ref>\n| [[2016\u201317 United States network television schedule|2016\u201317]]\n| style=\"background:#fc9;\"| #121<ref name=\"entertainment2017\"/>\n| style=\"background:#fc9;\"| {{TableTBA|N/A}}\n| style=\"background:#fc9;\"| 3.33<ref name=\"entertainment2017\">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/05/2016-2017-tv-season-ratings-series-rankings-list-1202102340/|title=Final 2016-17 TV Rankings: 'Sunday Night Football' Winning Streak Continues|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=May 26, 2017|accessdate=May 26, 2017}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Accolades===\n{{Anchor|Awards}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!align=\"left\"|Ceremony\n!align=\"left\"|Category\n!align=\"left\"|Recipient\n!align=\"left\"|Result\n|-\n|colspan=\"4\"|<center> '''Season 1''' </center>\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[5th Critics' Choice Television Awards]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/05/05/critics-tv-choice-awards-2015-and-nominees-are|title=The Critics' Choice TV Awards 2015: And the nominees are...|work=Entertainment Weekly|first=Shirley|last=Li|date=May 6, 2014|accessdate=May 7, 2015}}</ref>\n|[[Critics' Choice Television Award for Best Movie/Miniseries|Best Limited Series]]\n|''American Crime''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Critics' Choice Television Award for Best Actress in a Movie/Miniseries|Best Actress in a Movie o